                      @{b}@{bg shine}What's it all about then?@{ub}@{bg back}

    Blob is the ultimate in multi-player platform games. The aim of the
  game is to jump on the other player's head's, thereby scoring points.
  Each level has a time limit, and whoever has the most points at the end
  of the time wins the round. League points are then awarded, depending
  on how well you did in the round, how many people you killed and how
  many bonuses you collected. After a set number of levels the league
  scores are finalised, and an overall winner declared.

  Really cool bits about Blob:-

    EIGHT players simultaneously.
    Team games.
    No `lives', so no one ends up out of the action for ages.
    A multitude of bonuses for outstanding feats of gaming.

@endnode

