@node "Known Bugs"
@next "Credits"
@prev "Support"

                            @{b}@{bg shine}Known Bugs@{ub}@{bg back}

   When playing on an unexpanded A1200 with lots of players, glitches may
 start to appear (sprites flashing and brief speed changes). These
 problems seem to begin after you have playing for quite a while, not
 immediately. If this happens, quit out of the game at an
 appropriate point and then restart the game. This should solve the
 problem. Sorry, we don't know what causes it.

   I've also had some problems of late with it crashing unexpectedly
 at random times. This didn't used to happen and I'm not sure whether
 it's just my computer being a pain in the neck. Please send me a mail
 if you experience similar problems.

@endnode

